    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Why not show a demo of the examples part of the website (like the furnitures one) and link to that example page. We are currently showing an interface the user will not find anywhere on the instantsearch.js website.\n\nAlso add a small text like: \"Here's an example of what can be built easily using instantsearch.js and Algolia:\" then after the image \"Find this example on our website at http://...examples/...\" so that we are transparent on where we are linking.\n",
