    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Good point. I wanted to use the examples of the website at first, but I was struggling with doing an animated gif with nice enough colors (not dithered), and then I realized there is this gif we already use in several tutorials and slides we show at events. So I reused the same to stay consistent.\n\nSo instead of using an animated gif from the example page, why don't we add this example to the `/examples` page. We even have the full guide available on [instant search](https://www.algolia.com/doc/search/instant-search) demo. \n\nThat's another point, but I would also like to add more external examples/demo to that page like [marvel](http://pixelastic.github.io/marvel/), [steamdb](https://steamdb.info/instantsearch/) or [searchstone](http://searchstone.io/). \n",
    "created_at": "2016-05-25T22:23:09Z",
